{
  "stem": "20800.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Because before, it wasn't.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Before, they did only search.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it was understandable.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But when we come back, we have to do our mattresses-- put back, all the-- how do you call it-- beds making and all sort of things.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Because everything was a mess.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we have to make it good.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Straw mattresses--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--straw mattresses--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were in the-- in the-- of course, in the-- this cotton-like, dark cotton, remember.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it was mattresses.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But our leisure time, when we come from work, when we haven't got Appell, and they doesn't-- doesn't take us out, what we do-- we take off our things.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were knocking the lice-- lice.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We have lice in our clothes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we have to clean them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were killing-- we couldn't wash up.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We could wash once a week.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Can you imagine-- work like a horse all day, come home, not be able to take off and put something else, but to wear the same thing?",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sometimes we did, when it was warmer, we could do it at the-- night.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But-- and put on, when it's-- heater was on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it was half-wet.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we put in the morning and go to work.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So of course, we all had-- we didn't have hair.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But we have lice in the dress.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a big problem.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Or the-- oh, it was [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It-- comes sickness-- we have a lot of sickness of typhus because of that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They brought.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's why I had this-- you know how many people survived in hospital because I sent them there?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They would have been killed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We knocked this whole thing.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
